@ApplicationService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5002

### Get all applications
GET {{ApplicationService_HostAddress}}/api/applications
Accept: application/json

###

### Get application by id
GET {{ApplicationService_HostAddress}}/api/applications/{{applicationId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get applications by job id
GET {{ApplicationService_HostAddress}}/api/applications/job/{{jobId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new application
POST {{ApplicationService_HostAddress}}/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "{{jobId}}",
  "applicantName": "Jane Doe",
  "applicantEmail": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "applicantPhone": "+90 555 123 4567",
  "resume": "https://example.com/resumes/jane-doe.pdf",
  "coverLetter": "I am very interested in this position...",
  "yearsOfExperience": 5,
  "skills": ["C#", ".NET", "Microservices", "Azure", "Docker"]
}

###
